# Akasha ontology — sense/emotion bridges (proto-word wiring)
# Two jobs, so chains like  chocolate → sweet → (pleasure) → happy  traverse:
#  A. register the bare proto-words for perception (taste/smell/sound/touch/
#     texture/colour) and emotion, linking each to its hub atom.
#  B. link each perceptual quality to the emotion(s) it evokes — the valence
#     bridge that was missing for every modality except colour.
# Rule (as in concept_bridges.ak): ln <bare-word> <hub> rel — the bare word
# resolves to / creates the proto-word. atoms: 0 (links only).

# ── A. proto-word → perceptual quality ──────────────────────────────────────
ln bitter dna:taste:bitter thesaurus:related
ln salty dna:taste:salty thesaurus:related
ln umami dna:taste:umami thesaurus:related
ln savory dna:taste:umami thesaurus:related
ln spicy dna:taste:hot thesaurus:related
ln fragrant dna:smell:fragrant thesaurus:related
ln acrid dna:smell:acrid thesaurus:related
ln musty dna:smell:musty thesaurus:related
ln pungent dna:smell:pungent thesaurus:related
ln rotten dna:smell:rotten thesaurus:related
ln loud dna:sound:loud thesaurus:related
ln quiet dna:sound:quiet thesaurus:related
ln dissonant dna:sound:dissonant thesaurus:related
ln rhythmic dna:sound:rhythmic thesaurus:related
ln shrill dna:sound:high_pitch thesaurus:related
ln cold dna:touch:cold thesaurus:related
ln cool dna:touch:cool thesaurus:related
ln warm dna:touch:warm thesaurus:related
ln hot dna:touch:hot thesaurus:related
ln humid dna:touch:humidity thesaurus:related
ln freezing dna:touch:ice_cold thesaurus:related
ln icy dna:touch:ice_cold thesaurus:related
ln crisp dna:texture:crisp thesaurus:related
ln crispy dna:texture:crisp thesaurus:related
ln fibrous dna:texture:fibrous thesaurus:related
ln hard dna:texture:hard thesaurus:related
ln rough dna:texture:rough thesaurus:related
ln slimy dna:texture:slimy thesaurus:related
ln smooth dna:texture:smooth thesaurus:related
ln soft dna:texture:soft thesaurus:related
ln viscous dna:texture:viscous thesaurus:related
ln blue color:blue thesaurus:related
ln orange color:orange thesaurus:related
ln purple color:purple thesaurus:related
ln white color:white thesaurus:related
ln black color:black thesaurus:related
ln pink color:pink thesaurus:related
ln brown color:brown thesaurus:related
ln grey color:grey thesaurus:related
ln gray color:grey thesaurus:related
ln golden color:gold thesaurus:related
ln silvery color:silver thesaurus:related

